  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety of adding the investigational drug
      Motexafin Gadolinium to the standard treatment of radiation therapy and chemotherapy with
      drugs called 5-FU and cisplatin in patients with advanced head and neck cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
